-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository includes content derived from OpenUSD
(https://github.com/PixarAnimationStudios/OpenUSD), Copyright Pixar, licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (license terms at
https://openusd.org/license). The derived files retain their original
Pixar / OpenUSD copyright headers.

Derived OpenUSD content:

  - tests/openusd_compat/upstream/ — OpenUSD upstream test suites, copied for
    cross-implementation conformance testing against nanousd.

For clarity: src/nanousd/pxr_compat/ is original NVIDIA code — a shim that
implements a subset of the OpenUSD (pxr) Python API so that `from pxr import ...`
resolves against nanousd. It is not copied from OpenUSD.
